data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET! COZY BRICK HOME AT AN AFFORDABLE PRICE! Whether you are a first or second home buyer, this charming, cul-de-sac home is for you. This 3 BR/2BA ranch has plenty of kitchen counter space, laminate and vinyl flooring, and a spacious fenced-in back yard that is perfect for family gatherings and pets. Other attractive features include a .32 acre lot size affording privacy, and a 12x20 storage shed, with hurricane tie downs, and an open deck. This home has boundless potential! Schedule an appointment today.
